name: get_user_feed
description:
This is a sub-function API for tool instagram_v7.
Tool description: Get information from Instagram reliably
API description: Fetch the feed of an Instagram user using the provided user ID via the RapidAPI service.

is_id.description: The user ID of the Instagram account to fetch the feed for.

max_id.description: The maximum ID for pagination in the feed. Defaults to '2796754904080592191_25025320'.
